snippet.title: Conveyor Belt Sushi Simulator Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3536670/Conveyor_Belt_Sushi_Simulator/

Run your own conveyor belt sushi restaurant. Make sushi, serve customers, process payments, clean tables, hire staff, and design your restaurant’s conveyor belt. Set your own prices, manage troublesome customers, and expand your sushi restaurant.
